- 'summer break' typically starts around June 1;
- 'approved' means the project status is 'Approved'.

- "Projects" are like seeds planted by students in the academic garden;
- "Average rating exceeding 7" indicates highly rated projects;
- "Students who have planted more than one seed of creativity" refers to students who have submitted more than one project.

